OL,3,CBaby reindeer star among celebrities
OL,4,Ctraining for Soccer Aid at London
OL,5,CStadium
OL,7,FBaby reindeer star, Richard Gadd, said
OL,8,Fhe was thrilled to be picked again to
OL,9,Fplay for Soccer Aid after joining the
OL,10,Fstar-studded exhibition match last
OL,11,Fyear with celebrities and former
OL,12,Fprofessional footballers.
OL,14,FGadd shot to fame in the Netflix drama
OL,15,Fof struggling comedian Donny Dunn who
OL,16,Fworked in a London pub navigating the
OL,17,Fcomedy scene.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
