PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772550672
OL,3,CBaby reindeer star among celebrities
OL,4,Ctraining for Soccer Aid at London
OL,5,CStadium
OL,7,FHe offers a free cup of tea to a
OL,8,Fdistressed woman named Martha, a small
OL,9,Fact of kindness spirals into an
OL,10,Fintense and deeply unsettling stalking
OL,11,Fordeal.
OL,13,FSoccer Aid will be played at the
OL,14,FLondon Stadium in the Queen Elizabeth
OL,15,FOlympic Park.
OL,17,F"I'm a massive football fan," Gadd
OL,18,Ftold ITV News London.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
