FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772550672
OL,3,CBaby reindeer star among celebrities
OL,4,Ctraining for Soccer Aid at London
OL,5,CStadium
OL,7,F"It's for an amazing cause. UNICEF
OL,8,Fdoes such amazing work for children
OL,9,Fall around the globe.
OL,11,F"So not only are you having fun and
OL,12,Fnot only are you fulfilling sort of
OL,13,Fchildhood dreams, you're also doing
OL,14,Fsomething that's so important for
OL,15,Fchildren around the globe," he added.
OL,17,FThis year's match will be played on
OL,18,FSunday 31 May 2026 at London Stadium,
OL,19,Fthe home of West Ham United, kicking
OL,20,Foff at around 6:30pm.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
