PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772550672
OL,3,CBaby reindeer star among celebrities
OL,4,Ctraining for Soccer Aid at London
OL,5,CStadium
OL,7,FSoccer Aid was started in 2006 by
OL,8,FRobbie Williams who co-founded the
OL,9,Fevent with his friend Jonathan Wilkes.
OL,11,FRichard Gadd said it felt great to get
OL,12,Fthe chance to play in such a big
OL,13,Fstadium.
OL,15,FHe added: "I remember once doing an
OL,16,FEdinburgh Fringe show back in maybe
OL,17,F2009 and I had an audience of one and
OL,18,FI just took them for a drink instead
OL,19,Fof doing the show.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772550672
OL,3,CBaby reindeer star among celebrities
OL,4,Ctraining for Soccer Aid at London
OL,5,CStadium
OL,7,F"So to go from that to the capacity of
OL,8,Fthe London Stadium is huge, absolutely
OL,9,Fhuge.
OL,11,F"It's very surreal to go from one
OL,12,Fperson buying them a drink to say,
OL,13,Fsorry, but I can't perform the show to
OL,14,Fone person to going to 60,000 people
OL,15,Fin the London Stadium.
OL,17,F"So, yeah, it's very. It's a nice
OL,18,Fjourney as well to look back on, but
OL,19,Fit's very surreal at the same time."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
