PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772550672
OL,3,CBaby reindeer star among celebrities
OL,4,Ctraining for Soccer Aid at London
OL,5,CStadium
OL,7,FThe two teams are England XI vs World
OL,8,FXI and each squad is made up of former
OL,9,Fprofessional footballers mixed with
OL,10,Fcelebrities - actors, musicians,
OL,11,FYouTubers, athletes and TV
OL,12,Fpersonalities.
OL,14,FManagers are usually well-known
OL,15,Ffootball figures or famous names.
OL,17,FThe game will be broadcast live on
OL,18,FITV1 and online via ITVX and presented
OL,19,Fby Dermot O'Leary.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772550672
OL,3,CBaby reindeer star among celebrities
OL,4,Ctraining for Soccer Aid at London
OL,5,CStadium
OL,7,FHe said the simplicity of the event
OL,8,Fhelped make it so popular, adding:
OL,10,F"I think the message isn't
OL,11,Fcomplicated. Soccer Aid for UNICEF is
OL,12,Fthere to help children in the UK
OL,13,Faround the world, and I think that's
OL,14,Fan easy message for people to buy into
OL,15,Fbecause it's not political at all.
OL,17,F"And then on the day, you can properly
OL,18,Fenjoy this football match in this
OL,19,Fincredible stadium.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
