OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1772550672
OL,3,CBaby reindeer star among celebrities
OL,4,Ctraining for Soccer Aid at London
OL,5,CStadium
OL,7,F"We get to spend time in these
OL,8,Fincredible stadiums and we pack them
OL,9,Fso there'll be 60,000 people in here
OL,10,Fon the 31st of May.
OL,12,F"It's competitive, but a lot of
OL,13,Ffamilies come in and so there's a
OL,14,Freally lovely feel to it."
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
